title: AIIMS Gorakhpur Recruitment 2025 - Apply Online for 141 Senior Resident and Other Posts
description: All Indian Institute of Medical Sciences, Rajkot (AIIMS Gorakhpur) has officially released the notification to fill the vacancies of 141 Senior Resident, Professor, Additional Professor, Associate Professor, Assistant Professor Posts. Interested and eligible candidates can use this opportunity to apply for these posts before the last date of application.
